    "en": {
      "title": "The opposition calls for a debate on the attack on the activists",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The main organizer of the opposition Mr. Lakshman Kiriella has requested the Prime Minister Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena to convene the Parliament next Monday (25).",
        "He has also requested to hold an urgent debate on the incident of assaulting the activists on that day.",
        "Parliament is scheduled to meet on the 27th as scheduled in the Parliamentary Affairs Committee."
      ],
